Ando forovipen (politika) ek '''sherutno foro''' si o [[foro]] kai beshel o [[xulyaripen]] le [[them]]esko vai ek kotor themesko.

Butvar o sherutno foro si vi o bareder, o mai importanto foro thanesko. Shai te avel o mashkar katar shirdyas (astardyas) te kideren sa le riga kothar ando ek phandlo them. Si sherutne forurya kerdine te aven numa ek xulayaripnasko than dur katar e importante forurya le themeske, sar [[Canberra]] andar [[Australiya]] vai [[Ottawa]] andar [[Kanada]].

==Thema le buteder sherutne forurenca==
{{dikhvi|Patrinipen le themengo le buteder sherutne forurenca}}

Si thema so len si len buteder sherutne forurya. Sar misalyake, andi [[Afrika le Sudosko]] o administratikano sherutno foro si kai [[Pretoriya]] o foro le zakonurengo kai [[Cape Town]] thai le krisako foro kai [[Bloemfontein]].

==Le bareder sherutne forurya==
[[Image:Capital not largest city.PNG|thumb|Thema kai o sherutno foro nai o bareder foro]]
Butvar ek sherutno foro nai o bareder foro le themesko. Le bareder sherutne forurya ando fishtesavo [[kontinento]] si:

* [[Afrika]]: [[Kairo]] (11,146,000)
* [[Asiya]]: [[Tokyo]] (35,237,000)
* [[Europa]]: [[Moscov]] (13,600,000)
* [[Nordutni Amerika]]: [[Mexico (foro)]] (17,809,471)
* [[Ocheaniya]]: [[Wellington]] (445,400)
* [[Sudutni Amerika]]: [[Buenos Aires]] (14,230,000)

